14:32.289 --> 14:33.415
Chatty. Very chatty.

14:33.916 --> 14:35.834
YAO: Here. This is our pool area.

14:35.834 --> 14:37.753
FRANCES: This is nice.
‐ And the, uh‐‐

14:37.753 --> 14:39.171
‐ Oh, God. You?

14:40.172 --> 14:41.381
‐ Crap.

14:42.508 --> 14:44.259
‐ You must be Tony.
TONY: Yeah.

14:44.259 --> 14:45.469
I gotta take a piss.

14:45.469 --> 14:47.471
‐ Your personal wellness
consultant will be back

14:47.471 --> 14:49.431
