if there's a murderer or a bear?

15:19.753 --> 15:21.880
BEN: Okay, logically,
if there's a bear or a murderer,

15:21.880 --> 15:23.173
what are you gonna do?

15:23.173 --> 15:26.218
♪

15:29.263 --> 15:30.639
[whirring]

15:31.139 --> 15:34.726
DELILAH: Breakfast, 7:00.
