like you want to take her for a spin.

31:13.957 --> 31:15.250
JESSICA: No.
‐ Oh, my heavens.

31:15.250 --> 31:18.170
Uh, that's not what I‐‐ I mean
I‐‐ You're obviously‐‐

31:18.587 --> 31:20.589
No. I‐‐ Look, I give you my word.

31:20.589 --> 31:22.925
"Thou shalt not covet."
[Jessica chuckles]

31:22.925 --> 31:24.968
I'm a‐‐ I'm a happily married man.

31:24.968 --> 31:28.764
And one of my‐‐ my solemn word.
BEN: Sounds good.

31:30.390 --> 31:31.725
‐ I might have to watch out for you.

31:32.601 --> 31:33.644
‐ Nah.
NAPOLEON: Yeah.

31:33.644 --> 31:35.646
Because my wife's a humdinger, too.

31:35.646 --> 31:36.939
BEN: Oh, yeah?
‐ Yeah.

31:37.689 --> 31:39.191
Yeah, she's pretty attractive.

31:39.191 --> 31:42.778
