‐ Who do you think you're kidding?

41:56.016 --> 41:57.893
I've become a punchline.

41:58.977 --> 42:01.688
‐ Tell me, why doesn't
he love you anymore?

42:01.688 --> 42:03.357
‐ I don't know.

42:04.399 --> 42:07.611
‐ Although I can get violent,
